# Slide 18: Student Management / Subject Management / Hall Management
- Manages CRUD operations for students and subjects.
- Facilitates hall details management based on capacity.
- Enables search and filter functionalities for efficiency.

# Slide 19: Exam Management & Allocation
- Enables exam setups and student allocation.
- Supports batch processing for large data sets.
