# Slide 21: Technical Features
- Utilizes DAO for database operations.
- Implements Validators to ensure data quality.
- Incorporates FSM for dynamic process handling.
- Includes BatchAllocator for effective student distribution.

# Slide 22: Future Enhancements
- Expansion of integration capabilities with other systems.
- Improved user interface with responsive design.
- Implementation of AI for smarter allocation.

# Slide 23: Conclusion
- The system significantly reduces allocation errors and improves efficiency.
- Supports dynamic management of exam resources.
- Ensures compliance with institutional policies.

